otal budget ($146.44 of $329.10). This is the primary optimization target.\n- **State regression bug:** sprint-status.yaml overwrote 17-1's status from `done` to `backlog`. Needs a guard on regeneration.\n- **Design risk:** `execSync` in WorktreeManager will block the event loop during parallel lane execution — needs async refactor before epic 18.\n- **Unattributed costs:** $50.51 (15.3%) in the \"unknown\" bucket from orchestrator overhead not tagged to stories."}],"totalDurationMs":81097,"totalTokens":34473,"totalToolUseCount":10,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2434,"cache_read_input_tokens":31789,"output_tokens":249,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2434},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
